The three contiguous signs of Taurus Gemini and Cancer differ from all the rest in that they rise and set hindfore- most. Because in Gemini the sun is in apogee, his motion is slowest in this and in the two adjacent signs 3 and this retardation is fancifully derived by Manilius from the reverse position of the signs

themselves.
